giving warriors different skills does not help with the problem of the warrior. for example the /shield command they got. it can be usefull, if the warrior and the person he's protecting know what to do (ie, the chanter needs to stay put and not run around so that they stay in range of the warriors shielding). but this does not do anything overall for warriors main job, which is on raids to hit enough to keep aggro, and be able to take the beating.<br />
<br />
sorry. i do like to see people with the gumption to see what they can do to help the system. but i've just beome too jaded over 3 years playing a warrior to see any help for the system soon.</font></p>
	
