	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >Overall, I like it. The "Innate discs" are something I've been pushing for for a while. I think you might just keep it simple and remove the offensive/defensive discs altogether, and at level 51 give Warriors access to a slider bar, which when set at 0 makes them complete defensive, 100 completely offensive, 50 at "normal."<br />
